## This directory contains two Python3 scripts:

- create_db.py - Create SQLite database in the file bookmarks.db
                 and insert two records.
- dump_db.py - Dump the contents of the table Bookmarks from bookmarks.db

## Bookmark table schema:

```
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Bookmark(
			ID            INT PRIMARY KEY NOT NULL,
			Title         TEXT NOT NULL,
			Path          TEXT NOT NULL,
			URL           TEXT NOT NULL,
			ADD_DATE      INT  NOT NULL,
			LAST_MODIFIED INT  NOT NULL,

			UNIQUE(Title, Path, URL)
		);
```
